---
---
<section class="section-sm">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
      <div class="badge mb-5">What makes it different</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary tracking-tight mb-5">
        <span class="text-cal-gold">Personalized</span> to you.<br/>Private by design.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-body text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        OpenMind isn't a generic chatbot. It knows your major, your career goals, your skills, and your courses &mdash; and uses all of it to give you advice that actually applies to your life.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Three pillars -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">

      <div class="card fade-in fade-in-delay-1 text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🧠</div>
        <h3 class="text-text-primary font-semibold mb-2">Your Profile</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Major, year, interests, career goals, dream companies, GPA target. Import your resume for automatic skill extraction.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card fade-in fade-in-delay-2 text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🎯</div>
        <h3 class="text-text-primary font-semibold mb-2">Tailored Advice</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          &ldquo;You need UX skills for PM roles &mdash; take INFO 214.&rdquo; Not generic. Based on YOUR resume, YOUR goals, YOUR courses.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card fade-in fade-in-delay-3 text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🔒</div>
        <h3 class="text-text-primary font-semibold mb-2">Runs Locally</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          No OpenMind server. Profile stays at <code class="text-text-body">~/.openmind/</code>. Resume PDF never uploaded. No tracking.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Before/After comparison -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6 fade-in">
        <div class="card border-border/30 opacity-60">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Generic AI</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary italic">&ldquo;I'd be happy to help you check your assignments. Let me look into that for you.&rdquo;</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-text-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">OpenMind</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-body">&ldquo;You've got 3 things due this week &#x1f4da; NLP midterm is the big one &mdash; 30% of your grade. I'd start there.&rdquo;</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
        <div class="card border-border/30 opacity-60">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Generic AI</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary italic">&ldquo;I notice you have an assignment with an approaching deadline. Shall I set a reminder?&rdquo;</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-text-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">OpenMind</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-body">&ldquo;&warning; bro that writing prompt is due TOMORROW 11:59pm. Have you started?&rdquo;</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-text-secondary text-sm max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2 mt-10">
      Talks like a Cal student. References Moffitt, Doe, Main Stacks, Free Speech Caf&eacute;. Says &ldquo;hella.&rdquo; Celebrates with &ldquo;Fiat Lux!&rdquo; &#x1f43b;
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
